  "texts": [
    "Supplementary Table 4 shows the statistics of the test datasets built using Cohort-Short and Cohort-Long.",
    "We also show the distribution of query groups in these test datasets in Supplementary Fig. 3.",
    "As shown, the distribution of the query groups is similar for the additional test sets and our original gold-standard dataset (refer to Supplementary Fig. 2).",
    "Table 4 shows the performance of the QA models.",
    "As shown, for both test datasets, the ClinicalBERT model performs with overall high scores, reflecting its competence in extracting information over time."
